more or less https://www.tasteofhome.com/recipes/beef-onion-piroshki/

saute:
1 lb 90% lean ground beef
1/2 large yellow onion
minced garlic
salt
pepper

mix with:
1C chopped spinach
6oz shredded havarti
3/8C sour cream
2T dry dill

stuff into rolled out 20oz of crescent dough (2.5x 8oz packages, 20 pieces)

egg wash: 1T water, 1 egg
bake 375F, ~14m

